name: GRONK volume 1 BOOK
description:
OFFLINE FOR A FEW WEEKS. (I just had a baby and dealing with the holidays! Back for order after New Years!)



this is the first collected gronk comic book!

the book is 62 FULL COLOR PAGES! the webcomic itself is in black and white online... but i've brought in colorist Kevin Minor and he's made the gronk strips look AMAZING in full color for the printed page! 

the cover is a thick, glossy stock. it's very pretty. :P

each book will be signed by me. if you'd like me to make it out to someone in particular, please make a note of it in the paypal notes.

name: "F**k You, Box" mini book
description:
OUT OF STOCK. BACK ONLINE ASAP. 

the lil' book about a swearing, grouchy cat that EVERYONE WANTS!

30 page mini book is about the inner dialogue of my cat. it's FULL of swear words and a cat with a bad attitude. it's not for children. in fact, i think it makes children cry.

the book is 5" x 4.75"... it is staple bound and it will look lovely tucked in the magazine rack in your bathroom.... because it is the perfect length to read from cover to cover while taking an non-strenuous crap.

name: "ABCDEF-YOU" mini book
description:
OUT OF STOCK. BACK ONLINE ASAP. 

Learn the ABC's of cat ownership in this lil' book all about CAAAAAAAATS. CAAAAAAAAATS! 

this 30 page mini book will teach you what it's like to truly own a cat... if you already own a cat, you'll be reminded that you brought cat ownership on yourself. 

the book is 5" x 4.75"... it is staple bound. it would make a lovely coaster for a frosty beverage after you're done reading it.

name: original CUSTOM 3" x 4" mini-painting
description:
OFFLINE FOR A FEW WEEKS. (I just had a baby and dealing with the holidays! Back for order after New Years!)

the mega-popular tiny paintings i do at comic conventions come to the internet! 

you can have me paint a favorite comic character, movie character, animal, beloved pet, food, person... whatever you can think of! 

these paintings are 3"x4" and are all done in pen and watercolor. it is done on card stock and the corners are hand-rouned by me!

 you MUST let me know what you'd like in the paypal notes! otherwise... i'm just going to paint whatever i'd like and you'll get a painting of a cheesecake... or a happy burrito. 

if it is a portrait of a pet/person, then you can send me a reference photo to katiecandraw at gmail dot com. i normally only do one character per card. i can do 2 characters/pets/etc. though!

the 3 samples images shown are very representative of what you'll get. this is not an elaborate drawing... but a fun little tiny painting! 

if you have a really elaborate idea for a mini painting, let me know and we'll see if we can work something out.

name: original CUSTOM 6" x 6" painting
description:
****UNAVAILABLE AT THIS TIME DUE TO HIGH DEADLINE VOLUME. TRY BACK LATER****


a CUSTOM 6" x 6" watercolor! (see the sample images for an idea of what style/look you'll be getting!)

a favorite cute food to hang in your kitchen?
a portrait of your pet?
a favorite character for your kids' room?
a favorite character for YOUR room?

this price is limited to 1-4ish characters (more are allowed depending on complexity. have 6 cats? i'll still paint 6 cats for this price in one 6" x 6" piece!). if you want every spiderman nemesis on one piece, we'll have to talk about a new price. e-mail me before you purchase. 

after purchase, send the details of the commission with your payment and send any reference photos to me!

custom 6x6 paintings ship withing 1-3 weeks after ordering. if you need it ASAP, let me know and we can work something out.

name: original art commission: 17" x 5" cute movie/book/tv scene
description:
****UNAVAILABLE AT THIS TIME DUE TO HIGH DEADLINE VOLUME. TRY BACK LATER****


you name me a scene from a movie, tv show, comic, book... whatever! and i'll paint up a 17" x 5" piece that's cute as can be! 

look at the harry potter samples i have posted... it'll be a bit like that :)

you can either put what you'd like me to paint in the paypal notes or e-mail me after you purchase it (katiecandraw at gmail dot com)

name: original art commission: sketch card
description:
****UNAVAILABLE AT THIS TIME DUE TO HIGH DEADLINE VOLUME. TRY BACK LATER****

this commission is for an original artist sketch card (a 2.5" x 3.5" card) by katie cook. please include what you'd like me to draw for you in the paypal notes! 

the card will be executed in marker and watercolor, mixed with ink, colored pencil, etc. they are on my own card stock, with my information on the back. 

PLEASE let me know if you'd like me to draw the card in my more "cute" style or my more comic book style (sexier, etc). if you have a specific costume for a character in mind, let me know things like that too!

if you'd like a 2 or 3 panel card, e-mail me and we can work that out. also, if you want to order more than 5 cards, e-mail me and we may be able to work out a discount for multiple cards. 

the images shown in the listing are SAMPLES of the cards i can draw for you. they are NOT cards that i currently have available. sorry!
